        "text": "\u201cIf we could get a breed of gals that didn\u2019t care, now, for their young uns,\u201d said Marks; \u201ctell ye, I think \u2019t would be \u2019bout the greatest mod\u2019rn improvement I knows on,\u201d\u2014and Marks patronized his joke by a quiet introductory sniggle.",
