        "sentence_id": 69,
        "text": "\u201cO, Topsy, poor child, I love you!\u201d said Eva, with a sudden burst of feeling, and laying her little thin, white hand on Topsy\u2019s shoulder; \u201cI love you, because you haven\u2019t had any father, or mother, or friends;\u2014because you\u2019ve been a poor, abused child!",
