        "text": "Only groans, and people scuffing, and rolling round on the garret floor, half the night, from twelve to morning!\u201d  \u201cPeople up garret!\u201d said Legree, uneasily, but forcing a laugh; \u201cwho are they, Cassy?\u201d  Cassy raised her sharp, black eyes, and looked in the face of Legree, with an expression that went through his bones, as she said, \u201cTo be sure, Simon, who are they?",
