        "sentence_id": 40,
        "text": "The Christian is composed by the belief of a wise, all-ruling Father, whose presence fills the void unknown with light and order; but to the man who has dethroned God, the spirit-land is, indeed, in the words of the Hebrew poet, \u201ca land of darkness and the shadow of death,\u201d without any order, where the light is as darkness.",
